<PropertyList>

  <key><name>}</name><desc>autostart/autostop engines</desc></key>
  <key><name>c</name><desc>Open/Close canopy. You can click on the canopy handle to half-open it !</desc></key>
  <key><name>g</name><desc>Gears up</desc></key>
  <key><name>G</name><desc>Gears down</desc></key>
  <key><name>k</name><desc>Extend Speedbrakes (4 positions)</desc></key>
  <key><name>j</name><desc>Retract Speedbrakes (4 positions)</desc></key>
  <key><name>b</name><desc>Brake (wheels)</desc></key>
  <key><name>B</name><desc>Toggle parkbrakes</desc></key>
  <key><name>m</name><desc>Select previous mod</desc></key>
  <key><name>M</name><desc>Select next mod</desc></key>
  <key><name>l</name><desc>Toggle landing lights</desc></key>
  <key><name>L</name><desc>Toggle lights</desc></key>
  <key><name>o</name><desc>Acknowledge master caution</desc></key>
  <key><name>h</name><desc>Toggle night/day hud</desc></key>
  <key><name>ctrl-a</name><desc>Enable autopilot on Altitude</desc></key>
  <key><name>ctrl-s</name><desc>Enable autopilot on Speed</desc></key>
  <key><name>ctrl-h</name><desc>Enable autopilot on Heading (bug)</desc></key>
  <key><name>ctrl-n</name><desc>Enable autopilot on Heading (nav 1 radial)</desc></key>
  <key><name>ctrl-p</name><desc>Enable autopilot to keep current heading, altitude and speed</desc></key>
  <key><name>ctrl-P</name><desc>Disable autopilot</desc></key>
  <key><name>[</name><desc>Catapult launch (carrier)</desc></key>
  <key><name>]</name><desc>Toggle Launch-bar (carrier)</desc></key>
  <key><name>;</name><desc>Toggle Hook (carrier)</desc></key>
  <key><name>&lt;</name><desc>change phase for record loop</desc></key>
  <key><name>&gt;</name><desc>reinit record loop</desc></key>

  <text>
- take off rotation: 150kts
- landing: 130kts / speedbrake 40% / aoa 8
- taxi speed : 20-30 kt
- max speed below FL 100 : 250 Kt
- set altimeter to 1013 hPa over 5000 ft
- carrier take off : engage launch bar (]), unlock parkbrakes (B), throttle 80%, catapult ([)
  </text>

</PropertyList>

